00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:48,796
Beneath the noise of Kerning City's streets... power moves in silence. The Dark Lord does not walk among his people... he sends word, and his word is carried by careful hands. Nella is one such hand: loyal, precise, and NEVER fully transparent about her own purposes. When the swamp began to change and the monsters within it grew stranger... it was not the city watch that noticed first. It was the shadow network... which has ALWAYS paid closer attention to what lives below. The order went out not as a proclamation... but as a quiet commission... find someone new, someone without debts to anyone in this city... and put them to work.
